Global Binder-jet 3D Printer Market Insights
Binder-jet 3D Printer Market size was valued at USD 1.2 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 3.5 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 14.4% from 2024 to 2030.

Binder-jet 3D Printer Market Overview
The global binder-jet 3D printer market has experienced significant growth, valued at approximately USD 1.2 billion in 2024. The market is expected to reach USD 3.6 billion by 2030, growing at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 20.2%. This surge in demand is driven by technological advancements, cost-efficiency, and growing adoption across industries such as automotive, aerospace, healthcare, and consumer goods. The market’s expansion is also supported by increasing demand for metal printing and 3D manufacturing solutions for both prototyping and end-use production.

